{"tid":37044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼華人省長褻瀆可蘭經案開審數百警察戒備","createTime":"2016-12-13T06:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T09:15:10.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c6935796e22cd7ab9746f8aec0621c247555151","tid":37044,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161213/photo/bknint-20161213101906954-1213_17011_001_01p.jpg?20161213123803\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161213%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20161213101906954-1213_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20161213123803&h=5bdf2d28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印尼雅加達省長鍾萬學涉嫌褻瀆回教可蘭經一案，今日在雅加達中部的法院開審，大批強硬派回教徒聚集在法院外示威，警方派出數百人嚴陣以待。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161213/photo/bknint-20161213101906954-1213_17011_001_02b.jpg?20161213123803\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161213%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20161213101906954-1213_17011_001_02b.jpg%3F20161213123803&h=ef25d1a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鍾萬學上午抵達法院，他向5名法官鞠躬後坐在審訊室中央，審訊隨即開始；審訊期間，他一度拭淚。與此同時，數十名強硬派回教徒在法院外集會示威，他們揮舞拳頭，高喊「真主偉大」，不少人又大叫「可蘭經是我們的指引，立即監禁阿學（鍾萬學的暱稱）！」部分人則手持印有鍾萬學被關在囚牢內改圖照片的橫額。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161213/photo/bknint-20161213101906954-1213_17011_001_03b.jpg?20161213123803\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161213%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20161213101906954-1213_17011_001_03b.jpg%3F20161213123803&h=6e00b482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方出動大警察在法院外駐守，以防之前的反鍾萬學示威暴力事件重演。鍾萬學面對騷擾與褻瀆兩項罪名，騷擾罪最高刑罰是5年監禁，褻瀆罪是坐牢4年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161213/photo/bknint-20161213101906954-1213_17011_001_04b.jpg?20161213123803\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161213%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20161213101906954-1213_17011_001_04b.jpg%3F20161213123803&h=5f1883f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0acaff2eea5abdff14b64f6636e8a4efc153c690","tid":37044,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606ea277958c014740fc73e52823dc88a39018c9","tid":37044,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:03:51.000Z","msg":"輕輕地留名"},{"pid":"b41040136123f153bd9aa4f8b0126e74663fe6f2","tid":37044,"uid":7823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e29d39d1866ef3c43f7048c6cb3e55ab9a6ccc","tid":37044,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:09:12.000Z","msg":"華人<br />\n回豬<br />\n世界對決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05eac798e91ccd283621e3faa9b73481423a6143","tid":37044,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:09:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>華人<br />\n回豬<br />\n世紀對決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4f30aae82a35520b0e7ad65d7f1e029e2ae35eab","tid":37044,"uid":2818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:22:07.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ca4d90b87b54da14d63db524adcf25a6790488","tid":37044,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:23:11.000Z","msg":"回豬係世界最恐怖，沒有之一"},{"pid":"c2f524b269f377cdf8072ee450fe13f81a5dc1c3","tid":37044,"uid":10439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8506dbd8e6f6a71e2070c4f1895f8a41d1c255","tid":37044,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T09:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}